    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the tomatoes have softened, add your <strong>smoked paprika</strong>, <strong>roasted garlic paste </strong>and<strong> spinach</strong> to the pan</p><p>Cook for 2-3 min or until the spinach is starting to wilt</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1721219956202-x200.jpg",
